        <area aac="SA_FA001" description="South Australia" type="region">
            <forecast-period start-time-local="2026-07-23T21:17:39+09:30" end-time-local="2026-07-23T21:17:39+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-07-23T11:47:39Z" end-time-utc="2026-07-23T11:47:39Z">
                <text type="warning_summary_footer">For latest warnings go to www.bom.gov.au, subscribe to RSS feeds, call 1300 659 210* or listen for warnings on relevant TV and radio broadcasts.</text>
                <text type="synoptic_situation">A ridge of pressure system will build over South Australia this evening, with the associated high centre expected to lie over the Bight on Friday and Saturday. The high will move north over South Australia during Sunday, with a trough to build over the west of the State later Sunday ahead of a cold front to move over the Bight late Monday.</text>
                <text type="product_footer">* Calls to 1300 numbers cost around 27.5c incl. GST, higher from mobiles or public phones.</text>
            </forecast-period>
        </area>
